Debts to contributions to works
Social works in programs such as Habitat, Public Space Rescue and 3x1 for migrants may not be finished where there are serious delays due to the lack of economic resources, Miguel Ángel López Miranda said.
The Director of Municipal Social Development indicated that although the construction programmes have so far progressed, they are at risk, as the Government of the State has not fulfilled its obligations to provide contributions that exceed 11 million pesos in the three programmes.
